# Build And Deploy Workflow

For implementation tasks in this project:

- After completing the implementation, increment the app build number shown in the bottom footer UI.
- Then commit all intended changes with git and push them to the remote repository.
- Then push and redeploy the latest changes to Vercel.
- Treat this workflow as the default for code changes unless the user explicitly says not to commit or not to deploy.

Guardrails:

- Do not apply this workflow to read-only exploration, planning, or review-only turns.
- If the build number location or deploy target is unclear, ask before shipping.
- Mention the new build number and deployment result in the final response.
